      { name: 'Umeda', slug: 'umeda', lat: 34.7024, lon: 135.4959, group: 'North', description: "Umeda Station's underground mall network (one of Japan's largest) creates a unique climate refuge — the underground temperature remains stable year-round while the surface above experiences full Osaka weather extremes." },
