      { name: 'Ponsonby', slug: 'ponsonby', lat: -36.8533, lon: 174.7385, group: 'West', description: "Ponsonby's elevated ridge position west of the CBD catches prevailing westerly winds from the Tasman Sea. Its prominent café strip is frequently wind-exposed but offers excellent views across the Waitemata Harbour." },
