      { name: 'New Town', slug: 'edinburgh-new-town', lat: 55.9556, lon: -3.2021, group: 'North', description: "Edinburgh's Georgian New Town is slightly lower than the Old Town ridge, but its wide streets and exposure to northerly winds from the Firth of Forth make it one of the city's windier districts." },
